      p
        | Celebrate Together is a platform for everyone to write, read, and share knowledge. The nature of it&apos;s content might be funny, serious, offensive, or anywhere in between. While participating, it&rsquo;s important to keep in mind this value above all others: show enough respect to others so that we all may continue to enjoy Celebrate Together for what it is.
